    "description": "Built-Space domain machine for WELL-oriented accessible movement paths in the movement and fitness workstream. It monitors clear routes, ramps, elevators, door forces, and obstruction reports and emits AI-triggered outputs for verification, predictive optimization, operations work, and sustained compliant operation.",
